china national chemical corp
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Chemicals
Sub-Industry: Basic & Diversified Chemicals
China National Chemical Corporation manufactures chemical products. The Company develops, manufactures, and sells advanced chemical materials, specialty chemicals, basic chemicals, and chemical equipment. China National Chemical also produces agrochemicals, tire & rubber products, and other products.




