Responsible Care
Caring for the EnvironmentCaring for SocietyCaring for the EmployeeSustainability Report


Home > Responsible Care




 




Responsible Care



Caring for the environment With "responsibility and caring" becoming an increasingly important standard that global chemical companies should follow to maintain sustainable development, ChemChina actively leads the whole domestic chemical industry to "care for the environment". Responding to the call of "energy-saving and emission-reduction"Caring for Society To be the most respected chemical product manufacturer in the world has been the goal of ChemChina for years. In order to achieve that goal, ChemChina pays attention to its social responsibility and advocates responsibility and care in its business development. Caring for the employee At ChemChina, "caring for the employee"has become a strong part of the company's development. A central enterprise, ChemChina considers "caring for the employee" as one of its core values in every part of its development. 




